name: TRANSITION - DAY & NIGHT
description:
This is my work illustration participated for collaboration lucy enigma Project. Ansillustration as Illustrator and Lucy Enigma as a virtual musician. The title of this Lucy Enigma Project is Transition and i interpreted as Day and Night.

Day and night according to ancient Chinese philosophy is yin & yang, uniting nature and its contents with everyone's different desires or passions and goals. but the passage of time is unavoidable, so we must work hard and try before it's too late.

Written, Composed, Vocals  and instruments by Anggi @asteraspace#4926
Recorded at Kanawa Record Yogyakarta
Mixing & Mastering by Aloysiusnitia @AloysiusNitia
Studio Engineer by Kemal Akbar
Original Lucy Enigma MV art by Pram @apluswav
